net.frozencode.jniolib.misc

Class TimeoutQueue.TimeoutQueueNode<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.frozencode.jniolib.misc.TimeoutQueue.TimeoutQueueNode<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the element to be stored by this TimeoutQueueNode.
    Enclosing class:
    TimeoutQueue<E>

    public static class TimeoutQueue.TimeoutQueueNode<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    The TimeoutQueueNode class stores data for a single element of a TimeoutQueue and provides a method move its element to the back of the TimeoutQueue in O(1) time.
